      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project with this character-filled ride! While it's in poor condition and needs some dedicated TLC to return to its former glory, it offers a fantastic entry point for someone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle or a mechanical diamond in the rough. It's an honest car with plenty of stories to tell and is priced to move for the right enthusiast!",
