    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presented for the discerning collector, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintaining its original showroom luster, every component reflects a standard of care that transcends typical ownership. This is an uncompromising example of engineering excellence, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its debut. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
